{"body": "You don't need to open new pull requests all the time, especially to give a better commit message. Simply force push to the same branch that you opened the pull request on:\n\n```\n$ git commit --amend\n<write new awesome commit message>\n$ git push origin my_branch --force\n```\n\nGitHub will make the pull request have the proper stuff.", "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/comments/5821150", "created_at": "2012-05-21T12:26:21Z", "html_url": "https://github.com/rails/rails/pull/6422#issuecomment-5821150", "updated_at": "2012-05-21T12:26:21Z", "repo": "rails", "issue_id": 6422, "user": {"following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/steveklabnik/following{/other_user}", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/steveklabnik/events{/privacy}", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/steveklabnik/orgs", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/steveklabnik", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/steveklabnik/gists{/gist_id}", "html_url": "https://github.com/steveklabnik", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/steveklabnik/subscriptions", "avatar_url": "https://2.gravatar.com/avatar/233c279c012ebac792aaa805f966cbc7?d=https%3A%2F%2Fidenticons.github.com%2F0c22d45f31acf0f4192c8c12b7a55dee.png", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/steveklabnik/repos", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/steveklabnik/received_events", "gravatar_id": "233c279c012ebac792aaa805f966cbc7", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/steveklabnik/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "login": "steveklabnik", "type": "User", "id": 27786, "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/steveklabnik/followers"}, "owner": "rails", "_id": {"$oid": "523808a1bd3543c15100cc37"}, "id": 5821150, "issue_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/6422"}
